
 MPP Coursework: Reverse edge-detection algorithm
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

!--- Parallel Program ---!

  1. Compiling
  $ make

  2. Running
  $ mpirun -n NUM_PROC ./bin/imagempi IN_FILENAME OUT_FILENAME 




!--- Serial Program ---!

  1. Compiling
  $ make serial

  2. Running:
  ./binserial/imagempi IN_FILENAME OUT_FILENAME 


 
 where:
   - IN_FILENAME:   Name of input edge file (e.g input/edge.pgm)
   - OUT_FILENAME:  Name of output file (e.g output/out_edge.pgm)